{"tid":243960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再爆醫療事故！仁安遺留人工受精導管標記在病人體內","createTime":"2017-05-15T04:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T05:09:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbe15d04f4b71472ff966931904e2a1b75c33de","tid":243960,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"本港近日接二連三爆出醫療事故，仁安醫院今日亦公佈一宗醫療事故。衞生署於3月4日接獲仁安醫院呈報一宗醫療風險警示事件，涉及遺留人工受精導管標記於一名32歲女病人體內，她於3月1日接受宮腔內人工受精。病人於3月3日排出導管標記。衞生署在接獲通知後隨即跟進，並要求院方於4星期內提交詳細報告。院方已向衞生署提交詳細報告。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署審視院方提交的所有資料後，沒有發現有證據顯示該院在房舍、人手和設備方面違反《醫院、護養院及留產院註冊條例》（第165章）或《私家醫院、護養院和留產院實務守則》的要求，因而導致這次事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56695413&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56695413%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=71a968a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56695413%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=ea87fd08\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56695413&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"41fdbdc73e91711d614cbd877f0a53fc8f2f37b4","tid":243960,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"私家都唔見得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6449b46ba736c68c121a6f22c33bc546a87c32","tid":243960,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"已經記住咗捐精者嘅形狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}